Package: nsswitch-vpn
Section: utils
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Automates NSSwitch changes for Wireguard and OpenVpn DNS resolution
 Installs scripts to modify /etc/nsswitch.conf when OpenVPN (tun0) or WireGuard
 (wg0) by NetworkManager are activated or deactivated.